Process HISEA Input Data

Source: R/Final.R
process_hisea_input.Rd

Process HISEA Input Data

Usage

process_hisea_input(
  input,
  type = c("std", "mix"),
  nv = NULL,
  stock_col = NULL,
  var_cols_mix = NULL,
  var_cols_std = NULL
)

Arguments

input

Input data (file path or data frame)

type

Type of input ("std" or "mix")

nv

Number of variables

stock_col

Stock column name

var_cols_mix

Variables for mixture data

var_cols_std

Variables for standard data

out_path

Output path

stocks_names

Stock names

Value

Processed data
